{"title":"安装 Laravel 教程","date":"2014-03-07T16:00:00.000Z","link":"install-laravel-tourism","comments":true,"tags":["composer","php"],"categories":["代码"],"updated":"2020-04-15T21:36:20.851Z","content":"<h2 id=\"安装-composer\">安装 composer<a href=\"install-laravel-tourism#安装-composer\"></a></h2><p>composer 是一个 非官方的 php 包管理工具， Mac 下安装很方便：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">brew </span>tap <span class=\"keyword\">josegonzalez/homebrew-php</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">brew </span><span class=\"keyword\">install </span><span class=\"keyword\">josegonzalez/php/composer</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>如果这里报错提示：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">composer: Missing PHP53, PHP54 or PHP55 from homebrew-php. Please install one of them before continuing</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">Error: </span>An unsatisfied requirement failed this build.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>可以先执行下面的方法进行修复：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">brew </span>search <span class=\"keyword\">bison27</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">brew </span>install homebrew/versions/<span class=\"keyword\">bison27</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">brew </span>install php54-intl</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"安装-Laravel\">安装 Laravel<a href=\"install-laravel-tourism#安装-Laravel\"></a></h2><h3 id=\"通过-Laravel-安装\">通过 Laravel 安装<a href=\"install-laravel-tourism#通过-Laravel-安装\"></a></h3><p>首先，下载 <a href=\"http://laravel.com/laravel.phar\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Laravel installer PHAR archive</a>, 为了方便，重命名成 <strong>laravel</strong> 放进 <strong>/usr/local/bin</strong>。<br>之后，就可以使用命令 <strong>laravel new</strong> 在任何目录下安装 laravel 了</p>\n","prev":{"title":"火狐浏览器表单错误验证消息","link":"火狐浏览器表单错误验证消息"},"next":{"title":"产品平经理学习笔记-六大工作职责","link":"产品平经理学习笔记-六大工作职责"},"plink":"https://wuwb.github.io/install-laravel-tourism/","toc":[{"title":"安装 composer","id":"安装-composer","index":"1"},{"title":"安装 Laravel","id":"安装-Laravel","index":"2","children":[{"title":"通过 Laravel 安装","id":"通过-Laravel-安装","index":"2.1"}]}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"吴文斌","link":"<a href=\"https://wuwb.github.io/install-laravel-tourism/\" title=\"安装 Laravel 教程\">https://wuwb.github.io/install-laravel-tourism/</a>","license":"自由转载-非商用-禁止演绎-保持署名 (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}